<div class="page-header">
	<ol class="breadcrumb">
		<li><h4>Hansel and <%= @user.name%></h4></li>
		<li><a href="/intro">Intro</a></li>
		<li><a href="/dress">Dress</a></li>
		<li class="active">Breadcrumbs</li>
	</ol>
</div>

<div class="panel panel-default">
	<div class="panel-body">
		<p>So they don’t lose their way, Hansel and Ellie drop breadcrumbs as they walk.</p>
		<p>
		They need <b>1</b> breadcrumb for every <b>5</b> steps they take.<br/>
		It takes <b>30</b> steps to get to the end of the path.
		</p><br/>
		<p><b>If</b> they drop <b><</b> <input type="text" class="input_game" id="bc_answer_less"/> breadcrumbs <b>then</b> they haven’t got far enough.<img src="/img/green-check-mark.png" id="bc_answer_less_tick" class="tick"/></p>
		<p><b>If</b> they drop <b>=</b> <input type="text" class="input_game" id="bc_answer_equal"/> breadcrumbs <b>then</b> they get to the house.<img src="/img/green-check-mark.png" id="bc_answer_equal_tick" class="tick"/></p>
		<p><b>Else</b> they have gone too far.</p>
	</div>
</div>

<button id="bc_btn_answer" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg center-block" type="submit">Throw breadcrumbs!</button>